Use the standard library
This is how to search of lst:
   Remember that n is lst's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in lst
      Remember that count is 0
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this n times:
         When item j in lst is x, then:
            Increase count
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      When count is 2, then:
         The answer is x
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   Remember that neg1 is diff of 0 and 1
   The answer is neg1
